title: Education Minister says evidence of Aboriginal student attendance problems 'impossible to ignore'
text: WA Education Minister Peter Collier pledges to act on low rates of attendance among Aboriginal students at regional schools, saying parenting centres and Aboriginal kindergartens may help. ...
